<br>
1.  Tell them that they have to type /d so that the game will let you trade with them.  Accept duel and blow them up.<br>
<br>
2. TP them to Cazic and disband<br>
<br>
3. Give them 10000 copper and watch them try to get to a bank<br>
<br>
4. /ignore or just plain don't answer.  Not answering bugs them even more than getting ignore message.<br>
<br>
5. have them meet you 2 zones away to get stuff and don't show up<br>
<br>
<br>
